  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a clay tajine over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped green onions and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the smoked cobnuts, cumin, coriander, and paprika. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Add the couscous, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cover the tajine. Simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Fluff the couscous with a fork and stir in the coconut milk.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with additional green onions if desired."
